{"tid":717860,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"(unity)有冇巴打可以幫幫我依個大傻鳩","createTime":"2018-06-26T10:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T13:14:25.000Z","uid":5963,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4eae53ac3bd51e88cbf40f14e0b06d39316c2a","tid":717860,"uid":5963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:56:29.000Z","msg":"我係超級新手，問題係關於instantiate 。<br />\n<br />\n我想係遊戲既下面整一個spawner，然後spawn唔同既prefab，但我想依d prefab一個跟貼一個咁向上行，但依d prefab都係唔同長度，總共有4種長度。<br />\n<br />\n例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/183506_c83abe5f54aea04cb885a1a661287411.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F183506_c83abe5f54aea04cb885a1a661287411.png&h=936cf6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後因為圖入面左邊有粒製（大白點）禁左既話d車就會停，所以唔可以用time去搞（有錯請大大力屌）<br />\n<br />\n我依家有幾個方法，第一個係係camera下面既出面set一個trigger，只要一有車過就會spawn下一架，但係因為spawn係以prefab既original做正中間，所以就唔識set distance就卡住左，我有諗過set 唔同既spawn position 比對應既prefab，但整完之後唔知點先可以random spawn 依d prefab<br />\n<br />\n第二個係我係unity買左個asset叫liner breaker(好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，佢都係做緊類似既野，我睇左佢份script兩日但都係唔撚明，我一陣會share出黎比你地睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我係一個新手，我知我唔識好多basic野，雖然我上裝search得個幾日，但我真係好需要各位既幫忙，感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n總結問題係咁<br />\n1. 想知有冇方法可以改變prefab既origin point<br />\n<br />\n2. 點樣可以係一個script入面隨機spawn唔同既野，係特定既position，etc <br />\nrandom spawn cars A, B and C, <br />\nA只可以spawn 係0,0 <br />\nB只可以spawn 係0,-1<br />\nC只可以spawn 係0,-2<br />\n<br />\n3.有冇方法係可以直接令到d prefab意識到上一個prefab已經離開左有足夠既位置然後先spawn。<br />\n<br />\n4.如果有仲簡單既方法，真係希望可以大大力屌，屌爆我個屎眼，話比我知到底我有幾撚豬。<br />\n<br />\n5.講多聲多謝"},{"pid":"a13b530cd960463ebd700dabb846c5fdbd295a48","tid":717860,"uid":5963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:57:13.000Z","msg":"就係買左依個asset<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JAueLlcI83Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJAueLlcI83Y&d=Namzf7M27Ej1OBSDnrrH8L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=7f52d116\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JAueLlcI83Y</a>"},{"pid":"76970ac7b15cc6b2a21d07d57e13e9188897aa67","tid":717860,"uid":5963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a13b530cd960463ebd700dabb846c5fdbd295a48","tid":717860,"uid":5963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:57:13.000Z","msg":"就係買左依個asset<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JAueLlcI83Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJAueLlcI83Y&d=Namzf7M27Ej1OBSDnrrH8L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=7f52d116\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JAueLlcI83Y</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:01:44.000Z","msg":"入面spawn既方法同我既idea其實係一樣，都係random跟貼咁spawn出黎，我過一陣會post 部份script上黎，因為asset好似唔可以全部上傳，如果得我會upload成個包上黎都ok，仲有就係，我真係識極少極少，所以到時希望可以教教我，我知我好撚煩，亦無以為報，但真係希望肯理理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為我時間已經無多，對你地黎講可能係好撚快，好易既事，但對我黎講係一件重要既事，麻煩晒你地"},{"pid":"6c9b14871df75f2a95cde814150b6675f1a31c8f","tid":717860,"uid":5963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"去洗個碗，一陣返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as